1","memberstatus":"0","number":"676","dbdateline":"1547286286","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"42251258","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"老仓唯","authorid":"372961","dateline":"2019-1-12 17:59","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251115&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">rizutoaoitori 发表于 2019-1-12 17:44</font></a><br />\r\n也不至于吧……<br />\r\n我的理解是霙彻底“独立”了，不会再对伞哥哥过于依存。<br />\r\n不过二人联系少了这点倒真是…… ...</div><br />\n是在利兹与青鸟之前，三香刚毕业时的那次定期演奏会。这时候两人按动画应当是为数不多的如胶似漆的甜蜜时光","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"677","username":"老仓唯","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"677","dbdateline":"1547287179","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251267","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"老仓唯","authorid":"372961","dateline":"2019-1-12 18:00","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251077&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2019-1-12 17:40</font></a><br />\r\n短篇集里铠冢没有参与后面的演奏会啊，霙因为要准备而音大考试所以推掉了，伞木考完试之后还回来指导长笛 ...</div><br />\n第三卷最开始的演奏会，是三香刚毕业，利兹与青鸟之前啊。<br />\r\n说实话小说看得我感觉两人从头到尾都没有走到过一条路上，连“交点”都没有。武田绫乃的构思还是不太行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"678","username":"老仓唯","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"678","dbdateline":"1547287226","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251564","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-1-12 18:31","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251267&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">老仓唯 发表于 2019-1-12 10:00</font></a><br />\r\n第三卷最开始的演奏会，是三香刚毕业，利兹与青鸟之前啊。<br />\r\n说实话小说看得我感觉两人从头到尾都没有走到过 ...</div><br />\n哦哦那个演奏会，那确实<br />\r\n武田是这样的...波乱第二乐章前编后编也是。前编虽然利兹青鸟戏份很少，但是线索不是很清楚的。而且前后设定没法圆得很好。<br />\r\n山田在这个上面的构思比武田出色不少的。说白了就是，两人对希美和霙感情的定位不一样。山田就直接解读成爱情，武田并不是这样的。可以说一直在恪守友谊和爱情的边界，反过来是给明日香织疯狂加料，让读者一度假戏成真。<br />\r\n波乱第二乐章里用久美子当润滑剂这种事，就很明显反映出武田对希美和霙感情定位的冷淡和前景的悲观，山田这里的处理真的好太多了。俩人的事情就该俩人解决，找个久美子过来算怎么回事。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"679","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"679","dbdateline":"1547289102","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251617","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-1-12 18:35","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251115&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">rizutoaoitori 发表于 2019-1-12 09:44</font></a><br />\r\n也不至于吧……<br />\r\n我的理解是霙彻底“独立”了，不会再对伞哥哥过于依存。<br />\r\n不过二人联系少了这点倒真是…… ...</div><br />\n读到后面就一个感觉“貌合神离”<br />\r\n短篇里希美和夏纪那篇，还有穿插在前后的希美霙/夏纪优子互动对比，割裂感远比影片来得强烈，分明感受到的大概率就是两人会成为挚友，但绝不会越界了。<br />\r\n霙至少收获了成长和伞木给她的音乐，希美又收获了什么呢？谁又来理解她呢？武田就这么收尾了，至少目前是这样的","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"680","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"680","dbdateline":"1547289324","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251715","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"wuliaozheX","authorid":"389976","dateline":"2019-1-12 18:47","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251617&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2019-1-12 18:35</font></a><br />\r\n读到后面就一个感觉“貌合神离”<br />\r\n短篇里希美和夏纪那篇，还有穿插在前后的希美霙/夏纪优子互动对比，割裂 ...</div><br />\n武田似乎真的是往悲剧写的这段<br />\r\n不过没关系，我相信利兹与青鸟之后会改变想法的<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/065.png\" />谁不喜欢happyend呢","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"681","username":"wuliaozheX","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"681","dbdateline":"1547290024","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"42251845","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:02","message":"<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/065.png\" />小说算是BE，电影才是happy end啊，不知道武田会不会在三年级篇里发点糖<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"682","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"682","dbdateline":"1547290941","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"42251857","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:03","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251715&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">wuliaozheX 发表于 2019-1-12 10:47</font></a><br />\r\n武田似乎真的是往悲剧写的这段<br />\r\n不过没关系，我相信利兹与青鸟之后会改变想法的谁不喜欢happyend呢 ...</div><br />\n等一手番外或者决意第三乐章发糖好了，时髦值那么高的伞哥哥被武田无端迫害，看不下去<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/139.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"683","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"683","dbdateline":"1547291015","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251893","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"老仓唯","authorid":"372961","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:07","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251564&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2019-1-12 18:31</font></a><br />\r\n哦哦那个演奏会，那确实<br />\r\n武田是这样的...波乱第二乐章前编后编也是。前编虽然利兹青鸟戏份很少，但是线索 ...</div><br />\n我真是搞不太懂为什么宁愿久美子四处尬遇也不愿意写群像剧。北宇治这个舞台写群像剧明明很棒。而且还可以无限出短篇拖（<br />\r\n关于百合，我的理解，或者说我心中的百合是一种暧昧而又特殊的，不同于其他任何情感的情感，可以是只能在某种特殊的条件或环境下产生和存在。和GL还有一定区别。比如小黄和丽奈在我眼中绝对是百合，哪怕最后两人分别嫁给了老师和秀一，只要双方的感情还如高中一样纯粹就也是百合。但明日香和香织……怎么说呢，香织憧憬明日香我可以理解，但我看不到香织身上有什么吸引明日香的地方。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"684","username":"老仓唯","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"684","dbdateline":"1547291275","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42251908","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"老仓唯","authorid":"372961","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:10","message":"重翻这个楼，感觉本楼讨论了二十多页，唯一没改变的主题就是迫害伞哥哥。<br />\r\n从伞哥哥的领导能力到演奏水平，历史问题，自新态度，政治经历，情商社交，乃至恋爱生活全方位进行了批判。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"685","username":"老仓唯","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"685","dbdateline":"1547291419","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42252002","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:19","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251908&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">老仓唯 发表于 2019-1-12 11:10</font></a><br />\r\n重返这个楼，感觉本楼讨论了二十多页，唯一没改变的主题就是迫害伞哥哥。<br />\r\n从伞哥哥的领导能力到演奏水平， ...</div><br />\n发现了，像我作为伞哥真爱粉实在是看不下去<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/148.png\" />伞木这角色写好了时髦值绝对不低，有话题性，人设又好，声优演技也在线。要我说山田尚子就很懂，抓出个青鸟的故事出来改编，武田就比较直，是什么就是什么，不太能变通","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"686","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"686","dbdateline":"1547291979","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42252022","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"cauchua","authorid":"179356","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:21","message":"武田就是个写书的，她懂什么京吹<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/035.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 OnePlus ONEPLUS A5010, Android 8.1.0上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v1.3.2.1-fix-play","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"687","username":"cauchua","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"687","dbdateline":"1547292100","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"42252093","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"星野航","authorid":"505382","dateline":"2019-1-12 19:27","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42251893&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">老仓唯 发表于 2019-1-12 11:07</font></a><br />\r\n我真是搞不太懂为什么宁愿久美子四处尬遇也不愿意写群像剧。北宇治这个舞台写群像剧明明很棒。而且还可以 ...</div><br />\n你把久美子想成武田本人就行，换句话说，这是武田憧憬中的吹奏部生活。之所以她不愿意扔下久美子，是因为作者创作时候的代入感迫使并驱动她这么走了，换句话说，加入她把视角从久美子身上移开，她甚至可能写不出现在这种味道和感觉的北宇治。<br />\r\n我记得京吹刚出的时候，都在说京都魔改无敌，而且京吹剧情真正引人入胜的地方不算多，tv二期在我看来比一期更成熟些。主要称赞的地方还是演出效果和作画，也就是石原和山田的功劳。<br />\r\n一期里8话之后的剧情处理在于梳理了久美子被丽奈识破伪装和三年级遭遇变故的副作用两条线之间的脉络。交叉点就是香织和丽奈的竞演，这里的处理体现的更多是一种对梦想追逐的必然和社会性妥协的冲突。<br />\r\n二期剧情最好的地方其实是明日香线和姐姐麻美子线的交互，所以前四集出来的时候风评并不如一期那么好，反而让人觉得久美子一直在做剧情触发器。<br />\r\n比如二期第10话我真的很想打10分，花田大老师在这里把他对青春的理解用尽浑身解数写出来，真的太赞了。原作武田的表现力相比就确实差了一些。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"688","username":"星野航","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"688","dbdateline":"1547292477","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"42252645","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"nejiang","authorid":"160158","dateline":"2019-1-12 20:25","message":"一事无成伞木哥，时髦值哪里高了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/053.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我觉得伞哥的恋爱观很值得探讨，她一辈子拼了命的让别人喜欢上自己，却从未喜欢过别人，看别人问他约过没有，那个反应很值得玩味，大概她自己都想象不出自己爱上别人的情景","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"689","username":"nejiang","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"689","dbdateline":"1547295908","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"42252904","tid":"1797825","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2019-1-12 20:49","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=42252645&amp;ptid=1797825\"><font color=\"#999999\">nejiang 发表于 2019-1-12 20:25</font></a><br />\r\n一事无成伞木哥，时髦值哪里高了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我觉得伞哥的恋爱观很值得探讨，她一辈子拼了命的让别人喜欢上自 ...</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/065.png\" />希美外人看来等级太高了，打个比方就跟古利特里的六花一样属于“感觉是在和社会人交往”的等级，普通的高中男生怕是看到就要吓死了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"690","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"690","dbdateline":"1547297344","groupiconid":"13"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":[],"commentcount":[],"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum_viewthread","group_group","home_space","home_blog","forum_archiver","plugin"],"forum_threadpay":"","cache_custominfo_postno":["<sup>#</sup>","楼主",""],"forum":{"password":"0"}}}